    Discover modern, durable & luxury bags crafted for your lifestyle.
  </p>

  <a href="/products/allProducts" class="inline-block mt-6 px-6 py-3 bg-white text-black rounded-xl font-medium hover:bg-zinc-200 transition">
    Explore Collection
  </a>

</section>

